  "Description": {
    "English": "An <span class=\"name name-special\">extremely powerful</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Multi-Tool Scanning Systems</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potential upgrades include: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">scan radius</span> and/or significantly increasing the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">value</span> of <span class=\"name name-technology\">discovery data</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">多用途工具扫描系统</span>的<span class=\"name name-special\">极强</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块很灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">扫描范围</span>和/或显著提升<span class=\"name name-technology\">探索数据</span>的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">价值</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">多用途工具扫描系统</span>的<span class=\"name name-special\">极强</span>提升。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始安装升级。<br><br>内部芯片升级，增加<span class=\"name name-stellar\">扫描范围</span>，同时超额地提升<span class=\"name name-technology\">发现资料</span>的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">价值</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">工具組掃描系統</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">超強大</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能強化的項目包括：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">掃描半徑</span>和/或大幅提高<span class=\"name name-stellar\">發現資料</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">價值</span>。"
